{"tid":666131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）自訂車牌Benz司機不忿被抄牌，當眾狂吊，路過男串揸Benz就入錶喇！","createTime":"2018-05-15T15:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T18:32:44.000Z","uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"45b1fc9da3604c97fbb8795dd5f180743b086b46","tid":666131,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"泊車唔入錶，仲要眼超超？有網上片段顯示一名司機疑因入錶問題怒罵交通警員，最終有途人抱打不平，出口直斥司機：「你揸Benz就入錶啦」。<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期一（14日）發佈於社交群組「馬路的事討論區」，事發於旺角弼街，一名司機疑泊車後未有入錶，之後有交通警員「開咪」示意抄牌。司機遂在錶位前大罵警員：「你老X臭X，泊緊個位，你咪禮貌啲囉！咁X大聲，你小學生嚟㗎？」，交通警亦有嘗試回應。<br />\n<br />\n眼見司機愈鬧愈激烈，一眾途人亦加入戰團。一名男子直斥該司機：「人哋（警員）都係做嘢啫講真，你揸Benz就入錶啦」，另一婦人亦表示：「你鬧咗好耐喇」。司機見狀仍不心息，繼續喝罵警員：「你著件咁嘅蛤乸衣喺度揸車，你老XX，曬X死你呀！」警員則強調會繼續抄牌。<br />\n<br />\n網民直指片中司機：「好肉酸囉！泊錶位唔入錶」，認為「為左$2同$320，又何必呢」、「喺街又龍又鳳咁比（畀）人拍上網，啲尊嚴仲賤過$320」，亦有網民讚揚交通警「個阿蛇（Sir）幾好脾氣」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yea17oFZ-EQ&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYea17oFZ-EQ%26feature%3Dshare&d=l%2BKlAbT4fi%2BxrQMUUF1vPC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=31137b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yea17oFZ-EQ&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今鋪撐邊面？"},{"pid":"94e79f237a0a6a4439e7bc2af932c27b5b3a5f02","tid":666131,"uid":28237,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"講真，你唔係串77，一般呀蛇都個唔會搞你"},{"pid":"57d764e682057acd70824b62d96c3e3ce6fb6336","tid":666131,"uid":51205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"1 ON 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a498415b8327779473e7632f98ed5cd331d6807e","tid":666131,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"支持訂立辱警罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a30fe8850f2d1696b3ea7a30c42f8b8a40ad79","tid":666131,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:29:35.000Z","msg":"拉埋佢告佢行為不檢啦"},{"pid":"67bf81cd3413c62b57c7cb1281bad06149d79661","tid":666131,"uid":118888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"為左少少面就賠左人格，上埋蘋果仲要唔打格，咁就名留千古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59825ea5823a87c8129b6b51cc9894147c07835","tid":666131,"uid":118888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180516&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58197366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180516%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58197366&d=l%2BKlAbT4fi%2BxrQMUUF1vPC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2931fee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180516%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58197366&h=ed1db57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180516&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58197366</a><br />\n【爆相爆片】不滿交警開咪叫入錶 Benz男喪鬧：除衫隻揪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n底都起埋，出沒花園街賣手機殻「太子安」<br />\n車牌/樣乜都清楚睇哂<br />\n姐係同人講，黎屌我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6e4b9ad75d1ba9b96bc0c666c93ace85216e84","tid":666131,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67bf81cd3413c62b57c7cb1281bad06149d79661","tid":666131,"uid":118888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"為左少少面就賠左人格，上埋蘋果仲要唔打格，咁就名留千古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"啊好話聽日仲有冇人記得<br />\n就算幾個鐘後見到佢我都應該認唔到"}]}